title: Cheese Mukbang Disaster - Frenemies #9
description: On this episode of Frenemies Ethan and Trish return after a week off due to Ethan's COVID scare- and they celebrate with one of both of their favorite activities- EATING! Over food they discuss what they've been up to lately, if cow's milk is pus, jews, Trisha and Moses' relationship, and a whole lot more!
